---
title: Learn TunePad
description: TunePad is a free, online platform for creating digital music with Python code. This page provides learning resources including curriculum, tutorials, games, puzzles, interactive learning tools, and more. This materials is designed for learners who are new to both music and coding.
splash: /images/splash/homesplash.jpeg
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}
{% block header %}
    {{ super() }}
<style>
    article .content-wrapper {
        padding: 1rem 2rem 3rem 2rem;
        background-color: #f6f6f9; 
        margin: 0;
    }
    section.highlights {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #0002;
    }
    .logo-nugget {
        background-image: url('/images/quickstart.svg');
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
    }
    main {
        margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
    }
    header {
        width: 100%;
        height: 360px;
        background-image: url('{{ splash }}');
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block resources %}
    <div class="logo-nugget"></div>
{% endblock %}

{% block banner %}
    <div class="banner-text">
        <img src="/images/logo-black.svg" alt="TunePad logo" style="width: 130px; float: right; position: relative; top: -2rem;">

        <h1>Welcome to TunePad!</h1>
        <p>
            This site provides resources for learning how to create digital music using Python code.
            You can find TunePad curriculum, tutorials, games, puzzles, and more. 
            This materials is designed for learners who are new to both music and coding.
        </p>
    </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

<section class="highlights">
    <div class="resource-box" style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 10px;">
        <div class="card directory">
            <h3>Student Resources</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 2px 10px;">This is a student description. There will be information about why a 
                student should select this option and how curated content will help them learn.</p>
            <button>I'm a Student</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card directory">
            <h3>Educator Resources</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 2px 10px;">This is an educator description. There will be information about why an 
                educator should select this option and how curated content will help them teach.</p>
            <button>I'm an Educator</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="highlights">
    <h1><a href="/learn/">Getting Started</a></h1>
    <p>Our <a href="/learn/">getting started</a> activities are designed for beginners who are new to both music and Python programming.</p>
    <div class="cards">
        {%- for demo in collections.learn | limit(2) -%}
        <div class="qcard" data-url="{{ demo.url }}">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="{{ demo.data.splash }}" alt="{{ demo.data.title }}">
            </div>
            <div class="card-info">
                <h1>{{ demo.data.title }}</h1>
                {{ demo.data.description }}
            </div>
            {% if demo.data.audio %}
            <button class="card-audio-button">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                <audio src="{{ demo.data.audio }}" class="audio-preview"></audio>
            </button>
            {% endif %}
            <h3 class="level-badge">{{ demo.data.level }}</h3>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
        <a class="more-info" href="/learn/">Browse all {{ collections.learn.length }} lessons and activities &#8680;</a>
    </div>
</section>




<section class="highlights">
    <h1><a href="/tutorials/">TunePad Song Tutorials</a></h1>
    <p>TunePad <a href="/tutorials/">tutorials</a> give step-by-step instructions for recreating popular songs.</p>
    <div class="cards">
        {%- for demo in collections.tutorials | limit(4) -%}
        <div class="vcard" data-url="{{ demo.url }}">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="{{ demo.data.splash }}" alt="{{ demo.data.title }}">
            </div>
            <div class="card-info">
                <h1>{{ demo.data.title }}</h1>
                {{ demo.data.description }}
            </div>
            {% if demo.data.audio %}
            <button class="card-audio-button">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                <audio src="{{ demo.data.audio }}" class="audio-preview"></audio>
            </button>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="level-badge">{{ demo.data.level }}</div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
        <a class="more-info" href="/tutorials/">Browse all {{ collections.tutorials.length }} tutorials &#8680;</a>
    </div>
</section>




<section class="highlights">
    <h1><a href="/puzzlers/">TunePad Puzzlers</a></h1>
    <p>TunePad <a href="/puzzlers/">puzzlers</a> are games and challenges designed to sharpen your music+coding skills.</p>
    <div class="cards">
        {%- for demo in collections.puzzles | limit(4) -%}
        <div class="vcard" data-url="{{ demo.url }}">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="{{ demo.data.splash }}" alt="{{ demo.data.title }}">
            </div>
            <div class="card-info">
                <h1>{{ demo.data.title }}</h1>
                {{ demo.data.description }}
            </div>
            {% if demo.data.audio %}
            <button class="card-audio-button">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                <audio src="{{ demo.data.audio }}" class="audio-preview"></audio>
            </button>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="level-badge">{{ demo.data.level }}</div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
        <a class="more-info" href="/learn/">Browse all {{ collections.puzzles.length }} puzzlers &#8680;</a>
    </div>
</section>




<section class="highlights">
    <h1><a href="/interactives/">TunePad Interactives</a></h1>
    <p>TunePad <a href="/interactives/">interactives</a> are tools to help explore the connections between music and code.</p>
    <div class="cards">
        {%- for demo in collections.interactive | limit(4) -%}
        <div class="vcard" data-url="{{ demo.url }}">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="{{ demo.data.splash }}" alt="{{ demo.data.title }}">
            </div>
            <div class="card-info">
                <h1>{{ demo.data.title }}</h1>
                {{ demo.data.description }}
            </div>
            {% if demo.data.audio %}
            <button class="card-audio-button">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                <audio src="{{ demo.data.audio }}" class="audio-preview"></audio>
            </button>
            {% endif %}
            <div class="level-badge">{{ demo.data.level }}</div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
        <a class="more-info" href="/learn/">Browse all {{ collections.interactive.length }} interactives &#8680;</a>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="highlights">
    <img src="/images/splash/docs-splash.png" width="300px" style="float: right; margin: 1rem" alt="">
    <h1><a href="/docs/">TunePad Documentation</a></h1>
    <p>Ready to dig in? Read the <a href="/docs/">documentation</a> for all of the TunePad functions and modules.</p>
    <br clear="all">
</section>
{% endblock %}
